txt.en: 'My word, you could not have made it through this maze any more quickly! This old overgrown field seems to still be changing. Perhaps the maze will be different by tomorrow.'
The Wistmead wheat maze can be found in the Wistmead Harvest Festival space.\n\nErmentrude Haybank has challenged you to get through the wheat maze, from start to finish, before the time runs out.
<rgb=#FF0000>Reach the exit before the time expires</rgb>
The exit to the wheat-maze is around here somewhere... or is it?\n\nYou should try to find your way out of the wheat maze before the time runs out.

Ermentrude Haybank, the Maze-master of Wistmead, has challenged you to get through the maze before the time runs out. You must not tarry long within the wheat-walls!\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>NOTE: This quest will be removed from your quest log when the event it is associated with ends. </rgb>
Find your way out before the time expires

'Now that you know this maze well enough, and beat my challenge, how about a bit of fun? How fast do you think you could run through the wheat maze? I will allow you to cheat this time! If you beat this, you will be well on your way to becoming a maze-master!'
The Wistmead wheat maze can be found in the Wistmead Harvest Festival space.\n\nYou should talk to Ermentrude Haybank at the wheat maze entrance.
